
Welcome to Divine Diner!
Here is some sample dialogue entered into this system:

* [Read about Hestia and Aelius]-> Sample_Hestia_x_Aelius
* [Read about Zeus and Aelius] -> Sample_Zeus_x_Aelius
* [Read about Hephaestus and Aelius] -> Sample_Hephaestus_x_Aelius
